text: Hazel Creek may refer to: *Hazel Creek (Soque River), a stream in Georgia *Hazel Creek (Lehigh River), a tributary stream of Beaver Creek, Black Creek, and the Lehigh River north of Weatherly, Pennsylvania in Carbon County. *Hazel Creek (Courtois Creek), a stream in Missouri *Hazel Creek (Littleby Creek), a stream in Missouri *Hazel Creek (Great Smoky Mountains), a stream in North Carolina
title: Hazel Creek
